Name: Scribble Space
About the game: DRAW YOUR SHIP - FLY IT. Scribble Space is a game about creativity. Scribble Space is a little game where you can draw your own ship and then fly around the galaxy in search of the great Queen Space Bee! You'll travel various terrains and fight numerous UFO tyrants in this fun, action-packed arade-styled shooter! Like my stuff? Follow me on Twitter. @cotycrg
